HOST: https://api-game.lupus.com/

# lupus-game

The game microservice of Lupus in Tabula. This manages all the actions for the game.

## Join a game [/game/{game_id}/join]

+ Parameters
	+ game_id (string) - The game_id of the game to join

### Join a game [POST]

Request to join the specified game.

+ Request
	+ Headers
			Authorization: token SESSIONTOKEN

+ Response 200 (application/json)
+ Response 400 (application/json)
	+ Attributes (Error)



## Leave a game [/game/{game_id}/leave]

+ Parameters
	+ game_id (string) - The game_id of the game to leave

### Leave a game [DELETE]

Request to leave from a game where the user was in.

+ Request
	+ Headers
			Authorization: token SESSIONTOKEN

+ Response 200 (application/json)
+ Response 400 (application/json)
	+ Attributes (Error)



