## Game logic [/game/socket.io/]

### Require the socket [GET]

Require a connection to a new websocket where all the requests are made

+ Response 101

+ Response 400 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)



## Data Structures

### VoteUser
+ vote: USERID (string, required) - The votation of the user, it could be a user_id or something else

### Error
+ error: There was an error (string, required) - The error message
